{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234320/extras/About_the_game.png?t=1739299839\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome to the Demo, cadets!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s time to team up with fellow ghost hunters and take a stand against the mischievous ghosts hiding across the galaxy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spook-A-Boo is a couch co-op game for 1 to 4 players and is best played over <strong>Steam Remote Play</strong>. Coordinate with your friends and family to outsmart your spooky foes, and capture them before they escape. Race against time in the first 5 Levels to capture the pesky ghosts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234320/extras/Chase.gif?t=1739299839\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Use Cutting-edge Tech</strong> <br>Equip yourselves with the latest ghost-hunting gear to catch those pesky specters.  <br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234320/extras/Gadgets.gif?t=1739299839\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Encounter a Diverse Variety of Ghosts</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">These ghosts come in all shapes and sizes, their powers wacky and dangerous. Make sure that you catch them and not the other way around.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234320/extras/Electric.gif?t=1739299839\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Overcome Obstacles Together</strong> <br>Communicate, collaborate and strategise with your teammates to triumph through everything that is thrown at you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234320/extras/LevelMechanics.gif?t=1739299839\" /